1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to motor vehicles; to amend section 60-6,257,
2 Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska; to change provisions relating
3 to the luminous reflectance and light transmission of certain motor
4 vehicle windows; and to repeal the original section.
5 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
